name: SpaceX!! Version 1.0
description:
Welcome to SpaceX. You have one mission: you have to conquer all nine planets in the solar system.  To do this, you must wage war against the alien inhabitants of each of those planets. SpaceX is meant to be hard. SpaceX is meant to make you rage. Are you fit to lead the International Space Station? Can you take over the Solar System? Play. Play SpaceX to find out.

I hope you enjoy!
